text: Abadeh Tashk is a city and capital of Abadeh Tashk District, in Neyriz County, Fars Province, Iran. At the 2006 census, 6,213 people lived there. It can be Romanized as Ābādeh Ţashk, Ābādeh-ye Ţashk, Ābādeh-i-Tashk, and Ābādeh-ye Ţashk; also known as Ţashk and Ābādī-ye Tashk) == References == Category:Cities in Neyriz County
title: Abadeh Tashk
